Package editor.domain

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DatasetStatistics
    The class is responsible for handling all statistical queries of the sparql endpoint/RDF data uploaded to the VE.
    DataUpload
    This class handles potential datasets which will be eventually statistically analysed.
    LinksetAttributes
    The object which represents the information sent from the AngularJS side for the Linkset Void Creation.
    LinksetTurtle
    Main class for the creation of the VoID file for the Linkset descriptions.
    VoidAttributes
    The object which represents the information sent from the AngularJS side, for the Void Dataset description creation.
    VoidTurtle
    Main class for the creation of the VoID file for the dataset descriptions.
    VoidUpload
    This class handles the VoID uploaded by the users.
